{"tid":1723982,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"由五個月嘅狗暴到中大事件 - 論律法對權力制衡嘅重要性","createTime":"2019-11-15T10:43:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T18:54:35.000Z","uid":226562,"like":98,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"3061073a880057c4ec62b6cd5e77e2f44618c6ad","tid":1723982,"uid":226562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:43:15.000Z","msg":"老老實實<br />\n班狗可以搞到全城近七成人支持重組警隊嘅（民調）<br />\n最大原因係因為佢哋無紀律<br />\n應該話係狗隊前線冇咗紀律 有法不依<br />\n而狗隊高層到政府都不斷死攬佢哋 毫無依法問責處置之舉<br />\n所以班狗就一直係度作惡 變本加厲<br />\n由當初 612 亂棍毆打手足<br />\n到而家當街打咬普通市民 強姦謀殺<br />\n失去狗性<br />\n警暴問題歸根究底都係因為無需要對人民負責嘅政府唔對警察嘅權力作出法律所定下嘅制衡所致的<br />\n<br />\n而我哋作為一支追求民主自由嘅正義之師<br />\n係絕對唔容許犯下佢哋嘅錯誤<br />\n更加無好似佢哋咁犯下如此天大錯誤仲可以留係度嘅本錢<br />\n<br />\n睇返中大事件<br />\n雖然中大嘅手足於 1112 嘅大戰中大展雄風<br />\n成功抵禦班狗嘅攻擊（雖然係慘勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n但係係隨後嘅陣地戰中<br />\n就開始出現咗呢幾個月以來因為無陣地所以先無出現嘅問題<br />\n戰區內有唔少嘅紀律問題發生咗<br />\n例如炒車、爆校內建築物玻璃以至恐嚇使用火魔<br />\n呢啲都係對抗爭無好處而又會傷害到手足嘅行為<br />\n唔係一件好嘅事嚟<br />\n而個原因好大程度上係因為我哋無係一啲規則問題上攞到共識<br />\n<br />\n一開始提出不分化、不割席嘅方針<br />\n係為咗避免好似當年雨傘運動咁成班篤灰撚阻9住晒<br />\n給予手足升級行動嘅空間<br />\n但係咁樣並唔係一種對無紀律行為嘅默許<br />\n唔係俾手足可以胡亂使用武力嘅 consent<br />\n我好擔心如果唔對一啲大家共同嘅底線作出釐清嘅話<br />\n我哋都可能會好似班狗咁俾人唾棄<br />\n<br />\n所以我想係度提出下面幾點可能會比較多人接受到嘅條文<br />\n比較容易攞到共識嘅<br />\n拋磚引玉<br />\n希望大家可以討論到一個共識出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者再由各位 tg channel/group admin 係大家攞到共識之後再 confirm 一下<br />\n<br />\n1. 以下物件以及它的物件不受下列條文保護：<br />\n- 港共狗官及狗隊成員、以及其有關人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n- 對我方進行間接或直接傷害、以及攻擊我方之人士<br />\n- 對上述人士進行保護者<br />\n1. The following objects and its objects are not protected under the following terms:<br />\n- Popo, HK Communist officials and those related to them<br />\n- Those who directly or indirectly causes harm to us, or those attack us<br />\n- Those who protect the objects mentioned above<br />\n<br />\n2. 在非無可避免的情況下，不對我方人員及其財產使用武力。<br />\n2. No use of force in any unnecessary condition to our people, and our properties.<br />\n<br />\n3. 在任何情況下，不對民居底下的地舖使用火系魔法。應避免以火魔法進行裝修。<br />\n3. In any condition no use of fire magic to any ground floor shops under civilian house. The use of fire magic should be prevented in repairing service.<br />\n<br />\n（呢個應該再斟酌一下）<br />\n4. 應避免裝修純粹低調發表藍絲言論的店鋪。<br />\n4. Repairing service against shops that only had performed pro-blue speech in a low profile manner should be prevented.<br />\n<br />\n（呢個都應該斟酌一下，主要係針對應唔應該對清理路障嘅人士（港豬/藍絲）使用武力，好似俾方向報影到有手足攞箭對住佢哋）<br />\n5. 應避免對沒有作出攻擊行為的普通市民展示或使用武力<br />\n5. Use of force or show of force against non-attacking citizens should be prevented.<br />\n<br />\n下面交返俾大家討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e9bafd9ca41814cf02dd39328e6ec255b5b1c43","tid":1723982,"uid":226562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:48:37.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"aa20c077d1b90e72bf2ad724f562bfd17246d9ba","tid":1723982,"uid":226562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:57:23.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"ff4cc2213df168e72c095c20d1b65b30d6e5bd58","tid":1723982,"uid":226562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:22:07.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"000ccf6107d970d00483f028eaae118109a15ab2","tid":1723982,"uid":231647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:01:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"99a25543e067c98fc32813c7b64bc3ebef595540","tid":1723982,"uid":128261,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:05:43.000Z","msg":"寫得幾好，不過你要諗下點樣可以推廣，令大家遵守，但又唔會成為「大台」<br />\n類似既規則其實之前都有人寫過"},{"pid":"015c5f7be6f86cc9091aa0bce7f2fc36526f6526","tid":1723982,"uid":235283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:06:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c47c388cb77aab0a65901684697c4dea2387c5a","tid":1723982,"uid":226562,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"99a25543e067c98fc32813c7b64bc3ebef595540","tid":1723982,"uid":128261,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:05:43.000Z","msg":"寫得幾好，不過你要諗下點樣可以推廣，令大家遵守，但又唔會成為「大台」<br />\n類似既規則其實之前都有人寫過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:11:24.000Z","msg":"所以要係呢到傾下先<br />\n傾個絕大部分人都覺得接受到嘅版本出嚟<br />\n然後等覺 tg gp 再傾<br />\n然後等啲 channel endorse？<br />\n<br />\n其實民主政制就係咁<br />\n唔啱傾到啱<br />\n慢慢協商妥協先係出路"},{"pid":"c5bfa0a9a3904de733bb1c1cb4e3e381e29c52f1","tid":1723982,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:13:46.000Z","msg":"Seems legit"},{"pid":"79f91683c44d906baafe702ee4125dcf90dd697d","tid":1723982,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:15:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2cc3189ad7225579dea45f077dc2d235f4f4d97a","tid":1723982,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:15:20.000Z","msg":"Also respect the indigenous <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2400faeee2966c495fb58b3fcc27318baf1b18e3","tid":1723982,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:20:22.000Z","msg":"支持樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b87bcdb6882558327a3d330a6832f6e30ad2d20b","tid":1723982,"uid":123082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:28:52.000Z","msg":"共識對行動上係好重要<br />\n<br />\n推"},{"pid":"e1ab12d5ded77924bdbe6c54859b1b9e1d63663e","tid":1723982,"uid":226562,"like":0,"dislike